WEBVTT

00:01.330 --> 00:06.704
In the southeast of Peru, at more than 11,000 feet above sea level,...

00:07.047 --> 00:08.931
...lies the city of Cusco.

00:09.999 --> 00:12.823
The former capital of the empire of the sun...

00:13.217 --> 00:18.601
...is the gateway to the sacred valley and the long-lost city of Machu Picchu.

00:22.022 --> 00:24.169
Follow in the footsteps of the Incas...

00:24.560 --> 00:27.361
...and venture deep into the mystical Andes...

00:27.847 --> 00:30.905
...to see one of the most glorious places on Earth:...

00:31.631 --> 00:34.713
Machu Picchu, the city in the clouds.

